  "summary": "This proposal [ERC-7681](./eip-7681.md) delineates the integration of the fungible [ERC-20](./eip-20.md) token contract with the semi-fungible [ERC-1155](./eip-1155.md) multi-token standard, enabling cohesive operations between both standards within a single contract framework. It defines a mechanism for combining two token contracts and synchronizing operations between them.",
